    "When enabled, clicking a table in the sidebar will replace the current tab if it has no unsaved changes and you haven't interacted with it (sorted, filtered, etc.)." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
